  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><span style=\"color: #191813; font-size: 13px;\">Upon being imbibed, the mutagen causes the alchemist to grow bulkier and more bestial, granting him a +2 natural armor bonus and a +4 alchemical bonus to the selected ability score for 10 minutes per alchemist level. </span><span style=\"color: #191813; font-size: 13px;\">In addition, while the mutagen is in effect, the alchemist takes a &ndash;2 penalty to one of his mental ability scores.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #191813; font-size: 13px;\">If the mutagen enhances his Strength, it applies a penalty to his Intelligence. If it enhances his Dexterity, it applies a penalty to his Wisdom. If it enhances his Constitution, it applies a penalty to his Charisma.</span></p>",
